有期徒刑。\r\n施用第二級毒品者，處3年以下有期徒刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/111%2c%e8%8b%97%e7%b0%a1%2c86%2c20220223%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,111,苗簡,86,20220223,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"苗簡","JNO":"86","JDATE":"20220223","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例"}